    "attributes": {
        "action": "Stop childcare costs for parents on Universal Credit being paid in arrears",
        "additional_details": "The Big Issue has been campaigning on holiday hunger all summer. \r\nIt is a national scandal that children go hungry as they miss out on the meals they get in term time.\r\n\r\nWe at The Big Issue want to change that and make things better. For more details on The Big Issue\u2019s holiday hunger campaign, head here: \r\n\r\nhttps://www.bigissue.com/latest/we-want-to-know-how-youre-tackling-the-holiday-hunger-that-shames-the-nation/\r\n",
        "background": "One of the most significant factors driving the shameful spike in holiday hunger is childcare costs. Parents on UC must pay costs upfront before they are repaid in arrears, later. This leaves many struggling to pay for food and activities during the holidays.\r\n\r\nWe demand the government change this.",
